<----In PYTHON..Not in C..continue at your own risk.. :) --->

=====Remember : It's one-on-one chat ====

How to run ?

(on terminal)
step 1:
	python chatPipeServer.py
	--It will wait for text from client
	--once received, server can send text
	
step 2:
	python chatPipeClient.py
	--It will prompt for text
	--After inputting, wait for servers message
	
how to stop ?
	--both sides need to say 'bye' :P
	--the programs will terminate
